{"tid":1414534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"停止令黑警變為正義之師","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:43.000Z","uid":67292,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f72752d234cbee6e47d125a37749bfc77a37fc","tid":1414534,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"兩個月黎連場的發夢令警察既民望不斷下跌，警黑勾結同濫暴令大多數市民都企在我地果邊，而且願意理解抗爭者既訴求同想法。勇武同和理非既結合亦都令我地既光譜擴大到最大，甚至能說服淺藍市民一齊屌政府。<br />\n<br />\n但如果我地反黑警反暴政既同時，我地用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暴力</span>去對待無辜既市民。就係令警察由打鳩市民，變左做保護市民，由<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑警</span></span>變返做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">正義之師</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">諗清楚</span>，咩行為先對我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最有利</span>，咩行為先可以帶領我地爭取到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最終既勝利</span>。"},{"pid":"2d39f7b7a7d299120154034aa7a4d3ef37e1c3e4","tid":1414534,"uid":241458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"[機場防線] 再咁落去我地無可能贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414005</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"081c5ec13317649e6968a118ebc8a026ea0f6ce6","tid":1414534,"uid":18517,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:25:53.000Z","msg":"某一個行動究竟只係發洩，定係令我哋離目標更接近。"},{"pid":"08bf110737098768fede30e5a68a92b4c1ad65b8","tid":1414534,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:26:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8f3972fbc597b6577bf118c244b4bb2ea7ce545","tid":1414534,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"62476226aa933db2a3be633704c27d35027c0f70","tid":1414534,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:28:52.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3a885b3e4466157bc5847fa432a167ad535e1747","tid":1414534,"uid":251556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:28:57.000Z","msg":"黑警唔會變正義之師 但示威者形象一定會變差"},{"pid":"7954dcc01b0862efc0d7863d0f7ec3024aa54a5c","tid":1414534,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推推推 唔割唔割死也不割 但大家坐埋一條船 互相提醒守護啊屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"ee747511e55453d6f89fb621af97f2cc46ec5939","tid":1414534,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf43a71056ddeb80eb9ac327808e5e9651db520c","tid":1414534,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}